cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning framework that covers both Computer Vision and Natural Language Processing, indicating that it could potentially belong to multiple sub-categories. However, given that the focus is on implementing various models and making use of existing works, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are also likely given the specific applications mentioned. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are less likely but still possible given the nature of the paper.
